          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1690525473318-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>in 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[550ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, then add your <strong>soft cheese</strong> and a very generous grind of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> creamy</strong> <strong>stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1690525481711-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1690525481711-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1690525481711-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1690525481711-x1000.jpg",
