          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1690525491207-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leek and carrot are tender, add 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min, then gradually add the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and cook for 1 min further</p><p>Remove the <strong>gnocchi & chicken</strong> from the oven, pour over the<strong> creamy leek sauce </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Return the dish to the oven for 8-10 min further or until the sauce has thickened</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1690525498032-x200.jpg",
